=== Trophy ===
The main part of the trophy is a block of [[granite]], paying homage to Lombardi's college days at [[Fordham University]] as an offensive lineman when his offensive line was referred to as the "[[Seven Blocks of Granite]]".<ref>{{cite news|title=Michigan's Woodley wins Lombardi Award|url=https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/college/football/2006-12-06-lombardi-woodley_x.htm|access-date=July 16, 2017|work=USA Today|agency=Associated Press|date=December 6, 2006}}</ref>

